Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.52,1:42:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you become to make to make this a\Npossibility. It's a statistical rarity.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.71,1:42:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a statistical rarity and my\Nintention is that it should not be a
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.11,1:43:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,rarity.\NI think the means of accomplishing that
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.63,1:43:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,objective has not been available. The\Ntools weren't there. I don't think the
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.88,1:43:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,ego has ever been correctly\Ncontextualized.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.48,1:43:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's remained a block. In fact, the ego\Nas a block has been reinforced by re
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.08,1:43:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,traditional religion sets you up in a\Npolarized
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.48,1:43:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,uh guilt against your own ego. Now what\Ncan you do? You can only project it out
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.60,1:43:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,there. You can only become paranoid. You\Ncan only repress it. You can only go
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.76,1:43:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,into guilt. You can only try and commit\Nsuicide.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.60,1:43:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh you can drag yourself around and\Nself-punitive self flagagillation. That
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.88,1:43:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,was cool for a while.\NGuilt. Guilt. I tried it. I agonized in
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.63,1:43:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,guilt all through childhood, all through\Ncertain percentage of adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.56,1:44:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't get me enlightened.\NGot me an ulcer eventually.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.23,1:44:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think the way has been\Ncorrectly contextualized.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.23,1:44:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course what the great teachers of\Nhistory said nobody knows because much
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.28,1:44:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of teaching is non-verbal.\NIt's a positionality. It's a inflection
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.40,1:44:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of the face, a click of the voice. You\Nget the whole meaning with a
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.84,1:44:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,unsaid.\NSo what? So the students of the time
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.48,1:44:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,themselves were not enlightened. They\Nwere not really sp you know necessarily
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.60,1:44:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually advanced. So they tried to\Nmake the best then they didn't write it
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.32,1:44:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,down for a few hundred years.\NYou might forget a few things you know
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.96,1:44:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because\Nit's your great great grandson that's
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.32,1:44:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,writing this down having heard it you\Nknow u fifth hand and you miss you miss
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.88,1:44:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the inflections you miss the\Ncontextualization.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.23,1:44:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're taking the bare bones of what\Nwas said, now you're translating it
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.56,1:45:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,through different languages and then\Npassing it down for a thousand years
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.04,1:45:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,before anybody gets around to writing\Nit. You know, there wasn't any printing
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.00,1:45:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,press. So how we got as much truth out\Nof history as we did is beyond me tell
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.44,1:45:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you the truth.\NSo now it's a karmic um benefit of the
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.56,1:45:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution of consciousness\Nuh to have um understood or seen a
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.32,1:45:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,different way of contextualizing the\Nwhole problem. You see the evolution of
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.48,1:45:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness from its emergence on this\Nplanet. You see its development right
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.88,1:45:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,through the animal kingdom and you see\Nit right through the levels of man. You
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.56,1:45:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,see the levels of consciousness. Now\Nyou'll have a totally different picture
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.80,1:45:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of what your problem is for, you know,\Nwhat is spiritual evolution all about.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.44,1:45:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to be praying the rosary. So\Ntrue.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.11,1:45:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Used to be doing the rosary and going to\Nconfession and not eating meat on
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.04,1:45:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Friday.\NAnd then during Lent, you couldn't eat
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.28,1:46:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,any candy. I mean,\Nwhat's all that got to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.44,1:46:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NSo we tried to recontextualize a new way
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.52,1:46:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,a new way and\Nuh so I thank you for asking me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.67,1:46:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So we become united by commonality of\Nintention. If you and I have the same
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.04,1:47:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,intention now we're brothers already.\NEveryone here is my brother and my
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.19,1:47:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,sister.\NSo you're all my brother and you're all
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.80,1:47:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,my sister you know cuz we are one family\Nunited by the intention you know
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.28,1:47:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,intention will hold you together whereas\Nfamily ties may blow you apart
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.15,1:47:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you again. Yeah.\N>> Can we do a calibration?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.15,1:47:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Uh, the level of the group here,\NI need the the group today went up over
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.92,1:47:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,eight points, 10 points, 12 points. Wow.\N11 points. The group went up 10 points
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.36,1:47:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,today. That's the equivalent of two\Nlifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.36,1:48:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,>> 10 points is a huge jump of\Nconsciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.96,1:48:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelu\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.84,1:48:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.36,1:49:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
